Key Match Events: Ecuador went ahead in the 13th minute via a Jamaica own goal
Kendry Paez scored a penalty kick just before halftime
Alan Minda killed off the contest in the 91st minute with a goal from a counter-attack
Michail Antonio scored for Jamaica in the 54th minute
Post-Match Reflections: Victory gave Ecuador their first points of the tournament and leaves them level with Mexico
Jamaica is now eliminated following Venezuela's win on Wednesday night
